inic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtSvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=41cb83a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"145bef9cadeccbfec5f5d437dd73c9dd99f69406","tid":2032472,"uid":326526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"屋台最多藍屍五毛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473433046a10f5165d3d5dd78016ce655e4cbeea","tid":2032472,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"剛剛經過，仲係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565d52490d451808e1d62eb9f7403588bd1bf56b","tid":2032472,"uid":357591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"利害，香港人真係好有錢"},{"pid":"ced5aec66b68fb2c29e3f0988778e089f4af91bd","tid":2032472,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"接受現實啦連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95655f89641ab01657f2e96c69ce71c805c00663","tid":2032472,"uid":1156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":